\boxed{C} Based on the presented evidence indicating a strong sense of personal greatness combined with accusations of malicious intent from close associates, alongside the behavioral changes mentioned, the best fitting diagnosis appears to encompass both delusions of grandiosity and persecution.
\boxed{\text{C}}

